overview:
MAG-NET MEDIA HUB, LTD was developed and organized in pursuit of the following 3 missions.

  1. To develop and bring to market a new “Economic Development Strategy” that is capable of helping mankind overcome it’s current economic problems, thereby enabling mankind to enter into it’s next, and more prosperous “Economic Age”.

  2. To develop and bring to market (in support of mission #1) a new Directory-Based Search Engine and Media Portal (called “The MAG-NET MEDIA HUB”) that will make the internet more efficient, and make it “Easier and More Enjoyable” for people to “Find, Surf, and Access” the official websites of magazines and media sites on the internet.

  3. To develop and bring to market (in support of mission #1) a new “Locality-Focused” website format — that will serve as the “Geographic” Aspect of the MAG-NET MEDIA HUB — and is capable of connecting people to their local communities (via the internet), like no other “Local-Type” web resource ever has. The expansion of this network of MAG-NET LOCAL HUBSITES in every City, Town, Village, State, County, Province, and Nation of the world, is intended to be handled through the licensing of franchises to local newspaper publishers, media companies, and others, that currently operate in the geographic areas that they will serve, as MAG-NET LOCAL Franchisees.
